angers of a globalized, technologized world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 4aAmerican Studies. 4aBritish Studies. 4aFilm. 4aHorror. 4aLiterary Studies. 4aLiterature. 4aMedia. 4aNetwork Society. 4aVirus. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aAmerican Studies.  aBritish Studies.  aFilm.  aHorror.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aMedia.  aNetwork Society.  aVirus.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2021z978311076731540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839455593zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839455593423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839455593.jpg  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK